{"header":{"word":"מִרְמָה","entry":9115,"letter":"ר","strongs":4820,"page":941},"definitions":[{"title":"Def","body":" &#134; II. [[מִרְמָה]] ","content":"definition","show":"block"},{"title":"n.f.","body":" deceit, treachery;&#8212;abs. &#180;[[מ]]: Am 8:5 + ; pl. abs. [[מִרְמוֹת]] Ps 10:7 + ;&#8212;deceit, of balances, &#180;[[מאׁזְנֵי מ]]: i.e. deceptive balances Am 8:5 (&#8214;[[שֶׁקֶר ]]), Ho 12:8, Pr 11:1 (opp. [[קֶבֶן שְׁלֵמָה]]), Pr 20:23, &#180;[[אַבְנֵי מ]]: Mic 6:11 (v. [[[מאזן]]] p. 24); esp. treachery, craftiness, 2Ki 9:23, &#180;[[בְּמ]]: treacherously, Ge 27:35 (J), and (of crafty speech) Ge 34:13 (P); &#180;[[שִׂפְּתֵי מ]]: Ps 17:1 i.e. treacherous lips, &#180;[[לְשׁוֹן מ]]: Ps 52:6, &#180;[[פִּי מ]]: Ps 109:2 (&#8214;[[לְשׁוֹן שָָׁקֶר ]]), [[דִּבְרֵי מִרְמוֹת]] Ps 35:20, &#180;[[נִשְׁבַע לְמ]]: Ps 24:4 (&#8214;[[לַשָּׁוְא ]]); cf. Is 53:9 (&#8214;[[חָמָס ]]); also Ho 12:1 (&#8214;[[כַּחַשׁ ]]), Je 5:27, Je 9:5, Je 9:5, Je 9:7, Zep 1:9 (+ [[תָמָס]]), Ps 10:7 (+ [[תּׂךְ]]), &#8214;[[עָמָל ]] [[וׇאֶוֶּן]], Ps 34:14, Ps 36:4 (+ [[אָוֶן]]), Ps 38:13, Ps 59:19, Ps 55:12 (+ [[תּׂךְ]]), Job 15:35, Job 31:5 (&#8214;[[שָׁוְא ]]), Pr 12:20, Pr 14:8, Pr 26:24, Da 8:25; opp. [[מִשְׁפָּט]] Pr 12:5, + [[עֵר שְׁקָרִים]] v:Pr 12:17, + [[יׇפִחַ כְּזׇבִים]] Pr 14:25 (Hi Wild Toy read [[מְדַמֶּה]] for [[מרמה]] but II. [[דמה]] not elsewhere Pi); &#180;[[אִישׁ דָּמִים וּמ]]: Ps 5:7 (&#8214;[[דּׂבְרֵי ]] [[בָזׇב]]), cf. Ps 55:24, [[וְעַוְלָה]] &#180;[[אִישׁ מ]]: Ps 43:1; &#180;[[יַעֲשֶׁה מ]]: Da 11:23. &#8212;\r","content":"definition","show":"block"}],"notes":"","etymology":[],"morphology":[]}